data.description: GREAT CORNER LOT ON ALMOST AN ACRE!! Convenient to Everything, Beaches, Pensacola, Crestview!!  Roof Installed in 2021, Leach Field line Extended in 2007, tank recently pumped. New windows in back of home, and all new duct work installed with Extra insulation in attic. Water Heater installed in 2010 and A/C replaced in 2018.  Home has been maintained with major items.  Garage was converted to another bedroom in 2018 (permit was pulled).  Flat ceilings in living room and bedroom, tile installed in living room and hallway in 2013, other flooring is laminate. Split bedroom plan.  Kitchen and dining room combo with views into the wonderful back yard.  Yard building in great condition delivered in 2018. This would a great storage area
